      <title>红海航运危机给亚洲燃油市场带来震动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/red-sea-shipping-crisis-sends-tremors-through-asia-fuel-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[红海航运危机正在亚洲燃油市场掀起波澜，甚至提高了不使用水路航线的成本，同时促使卖家降低货物保费以抵消运费上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/red-sea-shipping-crisis-sends-tremors-through-asia-fuel-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 04:40:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
